This paper is about developing efficient algorithms for power system state estimation, which is a problem in control systems (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.LG, cs.NA). The paper also discusses the use of sparse connectivity in power networks, which is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC) and optimization (cs.OH).
